@startuml
title Journal Entry Transaction Lifecycle

hide empty description

state Draft
state PendingApproval
state Approved
state Posted <<End>>
state Rejected <<End>>
state Canceled <<End>>

[*] --> Draft : Create

Draft --> PendingApproval : Submit for Approval
Draft --> Canceled : Withdraw

PendingApproval --> Approved : Approve
PendingApproval --> Rejected : Reject

Approved --> Posted : Post to Ledger
Approved --> Canceled : Cancel

' Allowed loops/reverts for clarification
Rejected --> Draft : Reopen / Edit
Canceled --> Draft : Reopen / Re-enter

@enduml